         <abstract id="aspace_31199a2f96141d4974181e15e454ce72">The archives of Glen Lowell Jepsen are related to the Princeton collection. Notably include manuscrpt material, field notes and correspondence from 1928-1968 during which he served the Princeton vertabrate paleontology division and Geological Museum.</abstract>
